{"tid":402186,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中大警告即將拆橫額   學生會：廿四小時輪更守護   請同學一起守護","createTime":"2017-09-16T08:39:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T09:39:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"32e6ee3f3be922cfe374bf06c41b020beae41135","tid":402186,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T08:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170916/large/1505546422_b4b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170916%2Flarge%2F1505546422_b4b1.jpg&h=89565287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多間大學校園發民主牆近期均出現港獨標語，昨中大校長沈祖堯公開要求學生會盡快移除民主牆上的港獨語句，否則會由校方出手移除，但旋即已被學生會拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n屬於學生會管理範圍的中大文化廣場，寫著「香港獨立」的橫額已懸掛第11日，今午橫額仍高懸廣場，民主牆上的港獨標語也未被拆走。正在文化廣場守護的中大學生會副會長李振勇稱，學生會幹事會24小時輪更，每更6至7小時，以保護同學的言論自由。他指校方未有進一步通知學生會清拆橫額的事宜，若遇到校方強行清拆標語，會即時召集同學一同守護。  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170916/large/1505549134_bb47.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170916%2Flarge%2F1505549134_bb47.jpg&h=7afc72e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170916/large/1505549135_b6aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170916%2Flarge%2F1505549135_b6aa.jpg&h=bc197326&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170916/large/1505549136_d6bb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170916%2Flarge%2F1505549136_d6bb.jpg&h=5e64ee8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170916/large/1505549137_d049.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-p